snippet.title: Sherlock Holmes: The Devil's Daughter - Cinematic Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
A Mystic Trip whisks the master sleuth out of his stolid sitting room and hurls him into the vortex of an otherworldly adventure.

Sherlock Holmes: The Devil’s Daughter will be out on May, 27th on PS4, Xbox One and PC.
